OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,FIt's 8pm and Colchester's city centre
OL,7,Fis starting to hum with Friday night
OL,8,Frevellers.
OL,10,FThere are bars, pubs, restaurants and
OL,11,Fclubs getting ready to entertain the
OL,12,Fcrowd.
OL,14,FBut just as the nighttime economy
OL,15,Fwakes, less than a mile up the road,
OL,16,Fofficers at the city's police station
OL,17,Fpack out their gym hall.
OL,19,FThere are around 100 seats and a
OL,20,Fpulldown projector with the words
OL,21,F'Project Vigilant' on the screen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
