OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773342676
OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,FUniformed officers listen to the
OL,7,Fpresentation about aims and ambitions
OL,8,Ffor the evening ahead, with many here
OL,9,Fon shift till 2am.
OL,11,FIt's not long before they're on foot
OL,12,Fand in cars, on the lookout for sexual
OL,13,Fpredators who are loitering and
OL,14,Flingering in the shadows, ready to
OL,15,Fprey on vulnerable people,
OL,16,Fpredominantly women.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
