OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773342676
OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,FWe learn about the types of behaviour
OL,7,Fthey are looking out for: those who
OL,8,Fstare, stalk and leer at women, those
OL,9,Fwho approach women who are on their
OL,10,Fown or maybe drunk - and the ones that
OL,11,Finvade personal space.
OL,13,FMany of you reading will know the type.
OL,15,FThe key to tackling much of the
OL,16,Funcomfortable behaviour though, is the
OL,17,Fofficers hidden in plain sight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
