OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773342676
OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,FSome in that presentation had been
OL,7,Fdressed in civilian clothing, once
OL,8,Fdeployed, they feed back their
OL,9,Fintelligence to their uniformed
OL,10,Fcolleagues in real-time.
OL,12,FPlain-clothed male and female police
OL,13,Fofficers roam the city centre, just as
OL,14,Fthough they're members of the public
OL,15,Falso out for Friday night drinks.
OL,17,FBut all the while, they wait, watch
OL,18,Fand chat to observe any unsavoury
OL,19,Factions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
