OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,FIt's a key tactic of 'Project
OL,7,FVigilant', a Home Office funded
OL,8,Finitiative that's already up and
OL,9,Frunning at Thames Valley Police,
OL,10,FWiltshire Police and Norfolk
OL,11,FConstabulary.
OL,13,FToday, the Government has given an
OL,14,Fadditional nine forces across the UK a
OL,15,Fslice of #1 million, which it says
OL,16,Fwill now fund over 200 undercover
OL,17,Fdeployments across Kent,
OL,18,FHertfordshire, Gloucestershire, Essex,
OL,19,FSouth Wales, Staffordshire,
OL,20,FMerseyside, Cumbria and West Midlands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
