OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,FGood Morning Britain was exclusively
OL,7,Finvited to see Essex Police's
OL,8,Fdeployments in action, alongside
OL,9,FSafeguarding Minister Jess Phillips,
OL,10,Fwhose work in the violence against
OL,11,Fwomen and girls sector spans decades.
OL,13,F"I want women to feel safe," Phillips
OL,14,Ftells me.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773342676
OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,F"The whole point of this is that we're
OL,7,Fnot going to change our behaviour so
OL,8,Fthat bad men don't hurt us. We're
OL,9,Fgoing to make sure that we women feel
OL,10,Fthey can have a good time, at the same
OL,11,Ftime as making sure there's somebody
OL,12,Fwith their eye on the bad men."
OL,14,FAs part of the visit, the District
OL,15,FCommander for Colchester Police, Chief
OL,16,FInspector Michelle Sparks explains
OL,17,Fthey're also just as interested in
OL,18,Fthose in vehicles.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
