PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773342676
OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,F"Our officers are trained in
OL,7,Fbehavioural and detection techniques,
OL,8,Fin order to identify those individuals
OL,9,Fwho may be preying on vulnerable
OL,10,Fpeople," he explained.
OL,12,F"It might be they that approach a lone
OL,13,Ffemale, in order to try to befriend
OL,14,Fher, even though that contact is
OL,15,Funwanted, or individuals might be
OL,16,Floitering in taxi ranks."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
