OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773342676
OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,FGood Morning Britain understands that
OL,7,Fsuccessful actions have included
OL,8,Fidentifying a registered sex offender
OL,9,Foutside a popular nighttime venue and
OL,10,Fintercepting an intoxicated young girl
OL,11,Fbeing carried by a man she didn't know.
OL,13,FWork that Jess Phillips tells me is
OL,14,Fvital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
