PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773342676
OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,F"I've seen some deployments where
OL,7,Fthey've found somebody from just
OL,8,Fwatching their behaviour, gone back,
OL,9,Flooked up on the computer, found that
OL,10,Fthey were a known sex offender, gone
OL,11,Fto their car and found cable ties and
OL,12,Fropes in the back of their car, " she
OL,13,Fsays.
OL,15,F"That is terrifying, but it really
OL,16,Fgives me hope that this sort of
OL,17,Fproactive policing is the way forward."
OL,19,FThe hope is that by tackling these
OL,20,Foffences, officers can prevent future
OL,21,Fcrimes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
