OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FEvidence shows predatory behaviour can
OL,12,Fhave devastating consequences.
OL,14,F"The officers here tonight were told
OL,15,Fthat this isn't a small thing, it
OL,16,Flooks like looking out for weird
OL,17,Floitering, but I've seen where that
OL,18,Fleads to rape, murder," the
OL,19,Fsafeguarding minister says.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
