OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773342676
OL,3,CGood Morning Britain witnesses police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on predatory behaviour
OL,6,F"It's really, really important that
OL,7,Fpolice are out there thinking about
OL,8,Fpeople's behaviour, to stop that
OL,9,Fescalation."
OL,11,FNecessary work, when being a woman in
OL,12,FBritain still comes with risk.
OL,14,FBut this time, it's the predators who
OL,15,Fare being preyed upon.
